                                    to a stress-free day, including your shopping planning, collecting feedback about quality control and service delivery on our Website. These Terms also apply to applications downloaded from our Website unless otherwise specified in separate terms of use for these applications. Compliance with these Terms is mandatory regardless of whether the Website and applications are being used on a computer or mobile device. You must not breach any of the following terms or our Acceptable Use Policy set out below.

                                    <br><h1>User Content</h1><br>
